Is it worth the money? You better believe it! This game is, above all, a lot of fun and entertaining. It is a modern puzzle game that is reminiscent of old-school arcade. The graphics are clean and up to date. Each level is progressively challenging and difficult (48 levels + bonus levels). The developers of this game spent many hours of work with close attention to detail in an effort to produce a truly great gaming experience. You'll love it!

This game involves pushing a psychedelic cube around a platform in an  undefined part of the universe... somewhere in deep space. The Daft Punk of another dimension seems to have provided the soundtrack. Smaller cubes are there to help your speed, sometimes a dark cube threatens your very existence but our cube always makes it through.
